         <div type="translation">
            <p>The Council and the People honoured also after his death Epicharmos son of Chrysaor son of Epicharmos son of Chrysippos, a man who was munificent to his country.</p>
         </div>
         <div type="commentary">
            <p>Reinach noted that Chrysaor is a Carian name.</p>
